## Coverage Verification
<!-- All three checks must pass before Gate B. -->
- [ ] Requirements coverage = 100% (all requirements have at least one AC)
- [ ] Must-priority coverage = 100% (all Must requirements have at least one AC)
- [ ] Zero orphaned requirements (requirements without any linked AC)
- [ ] Zero orphaned ACs (ACs not linked to any requirement)

## Completeness Checklist
- [ ] Requirements coverage equals 100%
- [ ] Must-priority coverage equals 100%
- [ ] Zero orphaned requirements
- [ ] Zero orphaned ACs
- [ ] RTM version matches baseline version ({{rtm_version}} = {{baseline_version}})
- [ ] RTM reviewed and approved by Requirements Lead

## Handover Readiness
<!-- Confirms this RTM is ready for Gate B and will serve as the baseline for Phase 4 test planning. -->
- [ ] RTM version controlled and archived with baseline
- [ ] Test Ref column handed off to Test Lead for Phase 4 population
- [ ] All stakeholders aware that post-baseline changes require a Change Request
- [ ] RTM included in Gate B approval pack
